OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy cloud and scattered
OL,6,Fshowers, occasionally heavy at times.
OL,7,FSome sunnier spells, especially later
OL,8,Fin the day when showers will become
OL,9,Ffewer. Breezy, especially around
OL,10,Fcoasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLate sunny spells as showers
OL,13,Fclear away this evening. The rest of
OL,14,Fthe night will see mostly dry
OL,15,Fconditions, perhaps the odd light
OL,16,Fshower around northern coasts. Patchy
OL,17,Ffrost inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
