OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FFairly cloudy but dry for most
OL,6,Fplaces. The best of the sunnier spells
OL,7,Fare expected early in the morning and
OL,8,Flate in the day.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,11,Fcloudy with a few showery outbreaks of
OL,12,Frain on Monday and Tuesday. Best of
OL,13,Fthe sunnier periods on Wednesday,
OL,14,Falbeit rather breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
